          <li>Yu Z, et al. Targeted injection of ozone for treating lumbar disc herniation. Nan Fang Yi Ke Da Xue Xue Bao. 2012;32(2):243-6.</li>
          <li>de Nêuton F, et al. Effects of ozone in patients with chronic pain related to failed back surgery syndrome. Neuropsychiatr Dis Treat. 2013;9:1759-66.</li>
